print("""  The Pati-Salam model places one generation of fermions in:
  
  Left-handed:  (4, 2, 1)  under SU(4) Г— SU(2)_L Г— SU(2)_R
  Right-handed: (4М„, 1, 2)  under SU(4) Г— SU(2)_L Г— SU(2)_R

  Decomposing SU(4) вҶ’ SU(3) Г— U(1)_{B-L}:
""")

