#
# The charged lepton V_в„“ is nearly diagonal (small Koide angle perturbation).
# The neutrino V_ОҪ is nearly tri-bimaximal (democratic texture).
#
# Tri-bimaximal:
# |V_TB| = [[вҲҡ(2/3), 1/вҲҡ3, 0], [1/вҲҡ6, 1/вҲҡ3, 1/вҲҡ2], [1/вҲҡ6, 1/вҲҡ3, 1/вҲҡ2]]
# ОёвӮҒвӮӮ = arctan(1/вҲҡ2) = 35.26В°
